reviewText:
Showcases America's virtuoso fiddler in concert, on his tour bus and performing at the Lone Star Cafe in New York.  Songs include:

1) Orange Blossom Special

2) Will the Circle Be Unbroken

3) Handcuffed To a Heartache

4) Down Yonder

5) Silver Eagle

6) Every Song I Hear

7) How Does It Go

8) Move

9) Medley: Willie Ham/Alabama Jubilee/My Window Faces the South/Is It True What They Say About Dixie

10) There'll Be No Teardrops Tonight

11) Prove To the World
